overview: Lehmer’s Concord Buick GMC provides new and used vehicles to everyone in and around Concord. We specifically work with customers in Oakland, Antioch, Walnut Creek, Dublin, CA, and the entire Bay Area, to bring each and every one of them the best vehicle to meet their needs. When it comes to additional service, Lehmer’s is tough to beat. We provide the highest standard of financing in the area so that leases, warranties, and pre-approvals get met stress free. We also have a fully-stock parts department and service department available on-site for all your maintenance and repair needs. Contact Lehmer’s Buick GMC today and learn how we’ve redefined the auto dealership experience.
